title: NFL ATL: Week 15 TNF preview, disappointments
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 15 TNF preview, disappointments
description:
A room full of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling -- preview the Week 15 “Thursday Night Football” matchup between the San Diego Chargers and the Denver Broncos. The gang also gives you their biggest disappointments of the season.  Find out if Wesseling remains the owner of his beloved toaster in another addition of “Win Wess’ Toaster.” Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
